{"word":"διατάσσω","slug":"διατάσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>διατάσσω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:διά\">διά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:τάσσω\">τάσσω</a></el>, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:διαταγή\">διαταγή</a></el> and <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:διάταγμα\">διάταγμα</a></el>] the primary idea expressed through use of <el>δ.</el> relates to appropriate arrangement for securing an objective<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> <i>arrange, take care of</i> <a href='B:510 20:13'>Ac 20:13</a>; <a href='B:530 11:34'>1 Cor 11:34</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> <i>instruct, order, direct</i> <a href='B:470 11:1'>Mt 11:1</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:διαταράσσω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:διαταχθείς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}